<ab facs="#facs_245_r1l5"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr edel <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Sebolt <expan>pfıncʒ<ex>ing</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_245_r1l6">Durch <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd geweıſet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . daʒ er <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> klag ʒu </ab>
