<ab facs="#facs_245_r1l9">ſey vnd <expan>hınt<ex>er</ex></expan> Jm ſıcʒe vnd Jn beſlıeſſ etc <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jn ʒu </ab>
