<add><ab facs="#facs_245_line_1576666974040_8724">edel </ab></add> denn daʒ Jr ʒu dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Sebolt <expan>Pfıncʒ<ex>ing</ex></expan> ıcht ʒu </ab>
